            <title><![CDATA[【⚠️提醒！口腔溃疡老不愈合要小心口腔癌[吃惊]】口腔癌早期并不会有很明显的疼痛，早期表现包括反复出血、长时间不愈合的口腔溃疡、有形状或大小不一的红白斑...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【⚠️提醒！口腔溃疡老不愈合要小心口腔癌<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】口腔癌早期并不会有很明显的疼痛，早期表现包括反复出血、长时间不愈合的口腔溃疡、有形状或大小不一的红白斑、口腔内出现硬结肿块等。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒，抽烟喝酒嚼槟榔易诱发口腔癌，要戒除不良习惯，及早治疗烂牙、残根，去除不良刺激👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%88%B1%E7%89%99%E6%97%A5%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#爱牙日#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%9B%8A%E8%8A%82%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#人人公益节#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4948032563904535" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hi2ytunxwij61pq0yqb2902.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/jwlQOi8blx088KrB7VRK01041200gx5b0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1695230167&amp;ssig=q6DhYdD0Vx&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/PQhnJ9p0lx088KrAouoU010412008xwT0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps