            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E8%80%81%E4%BA%86%E6%8E%89%E7%89%99%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E8%80%81%E4%BA%86%E6%8E%89%E7%89%99%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#如何避免老了掉牙#</span></a>🦷】 据统计，我国35岁以上成人的牙周病患病率高达85%，因牙周炎导致的拔牙可占成人牙齿丧失总数的70%。若日常不好好防护，牙菌斑大量堆积，就会引发牙周炎，最终导致牙齿松动甚至脱落。👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%88%B1%E7%89%99%E6%97%A5%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#爱牙日#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%9B%8A%E8%8A%82%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#人人公益节#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4947954029756436" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hi2pu1xagfj60ne0v6ngq02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/kKVA02HClx088K6epGUM01041200uML70E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1695230177&amp;ssig=YMIBk1bimr&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/NmAf04swlx088K6eWR0k01041200hP0x0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1695230177&amp;ssig=qzxIjZd%2BEq&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/mLYpcqLxlx088K6eGPWU010412009GQL0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1695230177&amp;ssig=AsB4CyPZva&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://vi